                            <comment id="13152785" author="karlpauls" created="Fri, 18 Nov 2011 11:06:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Rats. This should be using adapt(BundleRevisionImpl.class) as this internal class doesn&apos;t return null if the bundle has been uninstalled. I commited a fix for this. Can you please test and close this issue if it works for you? Thanks a lot!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13154087" author="michael.hirsch" created="Mon, 21 Nov 2011 09:40:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This bugfix works for us. No NPE is thrown anymore. Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
